OL,3,CClaire's shuts all UK stores with
OL,4,C1,300 jobs lost
OL,6,FHigh-street fashion accessory chain
OL,7,FClaire's has said it will shut all 154
OL,8,Fof its stores in the UK and Ireland,
OL,9,Fresulting in the loss of 1,300 jobs.
OL,11,FThe move does not affect the
OL,12,Fretailer's 356 concessions, including
OL,13,Fmany in Asda stores, and its head
OL,14,Foffice.
OL,16,FThe retailer ` which is known for its
OL,17,Fjewellery, clothing accessories and
OL,18,Fear-piercing services ` was founded in
OL,19,Fthe US and first launched in the UK in
OL,20,F1996.
