OL,3,CClaire's shuts all UK stores with
OL,4,C1,300 jobs lost
OL,6,FIt quickly expanded across UK high
OL,7,Fstreets, but has come under pressure
OL,8,Ffrom low-priced online competitors in
OL,9,Frecent years.
OL,11,FThe closures come after private equity
OL,12,Fowner Modella Capital hired Kroll to
OL,13,Foversee the administration earlier
OL,14,Fthis year.
OL,16,FModella, which also owns former WH
OL,17,FSmith high street business TG Jones
OL,18,Fand Hobbycraft, placed the brand into
OL,19,Finsolvency after it was hit by
OL,20,F"alarming" weak Christmas trading.
