OL,3,CClaire's shuts all UK stores with
OL,4,C1,300 jobs lost
OL,6,FIt marked the second administration
OL,7,Ffor the business in a matter of
OL,8,Fmonths, having originally been bought
OL,9,Fby Modella from administration in
OL,10,FSeptember last year.
OL,12,FClaire's had already shut 145 stores,
OL,13,Fwith around 1,000 jobs lost, during
OL,14,Fthe previous administration last year.
OL,16,FA spokesman for Kroll said: "As of
OL,17,FApril 27, all Claire's standalone
OL,18,Fstores in UK and Ireland have ceased
OL,19,Ftrading.
